      "side": 1,
      "message": "yeah. experiments are file attributes, and file attributes must go before a package declaration, and an expression cannot have a package declaration.\n\nso the second example above uses an attribute, but it\u0027s not a file attribute, so it doesn\u0027t work as an experiment flag.\n\nbeing able to use experiments in expressions is a tracked issue here, which we need to think about separately: https://github.com/cue-lang/cue/issues/4297",
